name: 杰·辛瑟尔
introduction: Jay Sincere was born and raised in Houston, Texas. With his family being from Trinidad, Jay was raised with an affinity for acting and a charismatic love for entertaining others. Before his career began, Jay served in the U.S. Army for three years, stationed in Germany. After moving to Los Angeles in 2005, Jay began his career in acting, landing a variety of commercials, films and television shows. Jay is more recently known for his appearances in popular television series' Scorpion and Brooklyn Nine-Nine.
